1816.text: Episodes 1-3 are all individually better than every episode of the original doc with the possible exception of the final episode (the ending is just incredibly godlike and still makes me well up). The common thread of the series as a whole is very strong and compelling, still,

1817.text: Melee's story is never finished. Samox gave himself an extremely difficult task this time by taking a more timeline-based approach to the doc. It needs to render itself complete after Apex 2015 whereas we all today have the benefit of contextualizing it with almost 6 more years.

1818.text: Eps 4-8 have several problems. I think the vast majority of them can be fixed with low-impact editing. I think even Mango's image can be made more clear with good context clues. For me, it's mostly Leffen's presentation and the last 30 min or so that would be the hardest to fix
